Observatory - Class in galamsey
Observatory class with fields, methods and constructor to store and retrieve the name of the observatory, the name of the country in which it is located, the year in which galamsey observations started, the area covered by the observatory (in square kilometers) and a list of galamsey events that it has recorded.
Observatory() - Constructor for class galamsey.Observatory
Default Constructor
Observatory(String) - Constructor for class galamsey.Observatory
This constructor allows for observatories to be created when only their names are known.
Observatory(String, String, int, double) - Constructor for class galamsey.Observatory
A third constructor that takes into account the fact that most observatories will be created before the list of Galamsey events they register is established.
